- # Minimal layout for the in-iframe LTI launch landing page and the
- # top-level OAuth-redirect interstitial. We intentionally omit the
- # dashboard navbar and footer: the navbar reads `current_user` and
- # always renders "logged out" inside the Canvas iframe (cookies are
- # partitioned), so showing it would mislead any user who is actually
- # signed in to dashboard-testing in their main browser window. The
- # OAuth interstitial is transitional and auto-submits, so it doesn't
- # need full chrome either.
- content_for :head do
  = dashboard_stylesheet_tag('main')
!!!
%html{ dir: rtl? ? 'rtl' : nil, lang: I18n.locale }
  = render 'shared/head'
  %body.lti-iframe
    %main.lti-iframe__main{ role: 'main' }
      = yield
